| `batch_topk` | batch-coupled | blocked | 依赖 batch 共享预算 | 不兼容 |
| `adaptive_budget_topk` | batch-coupled / sample-coupled quota | blocked | 当前实现不是单样本静态导出 | 不兼容 |
